title: SAP HANA: Database Status
agents: linux
catalog: app/sap_hana
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the status of SAP HANA databases.
 To make this check work you have to install the agent plugin
 {{mk_sap_hana}}.

 If the status is {OK} the check is {OK}. If it's different than {OK}, the check is {CRIT}.

 This check is also cluster-aware.

item:
 The sid instance name and database name

discovery:
 One service is created for each instance.
